cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.MM, cs.SY, cs.CR 

This paper discusses the coordination of M2M communications, which is a subfield of networked systems and communication technologies. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also discusses the aggregation of data, which is related to information theory (cs.IT) and multimedia (cs.MM). The proposed strategy involves the use of D2D connectivity, which is a form of wireless communication and falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper discusses the need for resource allocation and congestion control, which is a subfield of computer security and cryptography (cs.CR).
